p.k: The team delve deeper into the macho fraternity of 'the Wolfpack' and soon find a darker side to the debauchery, secret hand signals and all-nighters that bonded the traders together. The Wolf of Wallbrook UK (2015). Cast: Denis Lawson, Dennis Waterman, Nicholas Lyndhurst, Tamzin Outhwaite. Director: Daikin Marsh.
